{"tid":158781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【假貨嘅嘢...】央視踢爆 Nike中國售air波鞋冇air氣墊！","createTime":"2017-03-16T13:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T01:44:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"897c02e51f1567812497060f56694e07abad3cce","tid":158781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170316/56435258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170316%2F56435258&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d1ba5827\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170316%2F56435258&h=3257793e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170316/56435258</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489637083_41c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489637083_41c1.jpg&h=30b7b028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">從央視的節目中發現，右邊聲稱有air氣墊的波鞋，鞋底竟然冇air。</span><br />\n中國假貨問題嚴重，但估唔到國際大品牌Nike都涉嫌造假！央視昨日「315」周年晚會的電視節目中，大玩踢爆，列出多個涉嫌造假的品牌，其中有指Nike推出的一款2008年北京奧運會特別版air波鞋，鞋底竟然係冇air氣墊！Nike方面已承認產品說明出現錯誤，並表示會願意退款。有網民就表示，全年只得一日可以對假貨一吐烏氣，其餘日子都繼續中伏。<br />\n<br />\n央視在節目中表示，收到一位叫郎先生的觀眾投訴，指其去年透過Nike官網，抽籤抽中，售價為1,499元人民幣的2008年北京奧運會的高比拜恩（Kobe Bryant）的復刻特別版波鞋，波鞋在產品說明中，指出鞋底有Nike專利的zoom air氣墊。不過郎先生表示，穿了這對air波鞋去打籃球時，發現對鞋着得不舒服，跳後落地後鞋踭會痛，懷疑鞋底的鞋氣墊是假貨。<br />\n於是郎先生聲稱他在鞋踭位切開一個小洞口，發現鞋底是無air氣墊。央視其後分別用一對有air氣墊的Hypedunk08及一對北京奧運版Kobe Bryant特別版波鞋做測試，將兩對鞋切開，發現Hypedunk08的鞋底有air氣墊，但Kobe Bryant特別版波鞋只得橡膠底。<br />\n央視又指出，郎先生在網上另外發現有網友都中伏，便組成60多人的「維權小隊」，向Nike投訴。Nike上海分店方面初初只承認在產品說明方面有誤導，並不肯作出賠償，並自行在網站刪除該對波鞋的介紹說明。其後事件鬧大，上海分店才承諾作出退款。<br />\n央視又指，Nike於2011年出售的Zoom 2011籃球鞋，亦被踢爆無air氣墊，被北京市工商局罰款487萬元人民幣。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489637084_9676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489637084_9676.jpg&h=41f7f96d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">售價為1,499元人民幣的2008年北京奧運會的高比拜恩（kobe bryant）的復刻特別版波鞋。</span>"},{"pid":"e29284457c63ddb3bb4eb07ad7abf12c443d3695","tid":158781,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"特別版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8045eb389421d2d33215f5c63f956d3873c30b2","tid":158781,"uid":2270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"大陸人on 撚9，錯體版先值錢ma <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ae3d38bb98ac8ee2948d733862444b59e2d5d4","tid":158781,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"又唔見支那人夠膽叫三鹿奶粉賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b903858f02d05a8ee4182a51ccf7f2356552f800","tid":158781,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔見支那人夠膽叫三鹿奶粉賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尋釁滋事,拉鳩你"},{"pid":"4511da785fcd2c55b88488883efa17ecae7d3392","tid":158781,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"除左支那製 全世界都有問題"},{"pid":"de8417c456776624a3c676bf842515e49b432e8d","tid":158781,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:18:25.000Z","msg":"Nike 今舖真係明玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知大陸有冇商品說明條例"},{"pid":"b9ab787a87dfa7c060ab6326bc7eca651d0d0840","tid":158781,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/201