=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n維權玩命二字"},{"pid":"f67422b707a4e1b2cc499e59ff2607afd447f45e","tid":158781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b57845be547119921d3237945cf943eb9227843","tid":158781,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:37:23.000Z","msg":"睇新聞央視針對果堆都係外國牌...唔見佢捉下自己國家D牌子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167af38fd543bed17665541f86ccc104148cde79","tid":158781,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇新聞央視針對果堆都係外國牌...唔見佢捉下自己國家D牌子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那邏輯，錯的是世界"}]}